    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/8de65a48461e3b5fcb32d9d0ec0c5eb1.poster.avif?t=1764457855\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/8de65a48461e3b5fcb32d9d0ec0c5eb1.webm?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/8de65a48461e3b5fcb32d9d0ec0c5eb1.mp4?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manners Be Damned!</strong> 是一款沙发合作派对游戏，你和最多 7 位朋友将在一座古老而致命的神庙中进行平台闯关挑战。你们唯一拥有的工具是优雅的手杖——非常适合把对手推入险境！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/3fdf355dbd4273a775d9939ca26b7def.poster.avif?t=1764457855\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/3fdf355dbd4273a775d9939ca26b7def.webm?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/3fdf355dbd4273a775d9939ca26b7def.mp4?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但别担心！这里的死亡代价很低——所以尽情放手去拼，用最快的节奏来获取任何优势。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/bcc035d91c48dfedc42ee9f08be837a1.poster.avif?t=1764457855\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/bcc035d91c48dfedc42ee9f08be837a1.webm?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/bcc035d91c48dfedc42ee9f08be837a1.mp4?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过展现你的速度、灵活度以及对手杖的熟练掌控来获得积分，证明你才是最强的绅士！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/345eb8a7f7d9d02891fe17e468564504.poster.avif?t=1764457855\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/345eb8a7f7d9d02891fe17e468564504.webm?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258940/extras/345eb8a7f7d9d02891fe17e468564504.mp4?t=1764457855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地合作，最多支持 8 位玩家（可通过 Steam Remote Play Together 进行线上游玩）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两种独特的游戏模式（“King of the Hat”和“Temple Dash”）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爆笑的玩家互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100% 语音录制音效</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有人都能轻松上手，适合各个年龄和水平</p></li></ul>",
